<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_118" id="58r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_118_r1l9"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Grefen ʒu velldencʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_118_r1l10">vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ʒu Meyſenheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_118_r1l11"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> . vns hat <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> lıeber <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> vnd Ratgeſelle vvılhelm Mendell </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_118_r1l12">wol geſagt / vvıe ſıch eẅr mechtıkeıt / als er mıt <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> nehſt ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_118_r1l13">Frankfurt / von des handels <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ʒwıſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_118_r1l14">Stepfan von Peyern vnd vnſer von <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> ein ſeinr <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> Jüdınn vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_118_r1l15">einr Jüdinn bey vns wonhaft . geredt hab . <expan>gnedıklıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab beweıſet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_118_r1l16">des wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> mechtıkeıt <expan>fleıſſıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> danken vnd wıllıklıch begern <expan>ʒuu<ex>er</ex></expan> = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_118_r1l17">dıenen / Alſo ſchıken wır <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvılhelm Mendell ʒu <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_118_r1l18">dem wir befolhen <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mıt <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> / bas von <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>ſache<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_118_r1l19">reden . Vnd <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>mechtık<ex>eit</ex></expan> mıt fleıſſ / VVas <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> Ratgeſelle </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_118_r1l20">in <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>ſache<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu dıſem mal von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an eẅr gnade <expan>w<ex>er</ex>be</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_118_r1l21">Daʒ Jr Jn vmb <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> darinn günſtıklıch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan> . Jm des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_118_r1l22">gencʒlıch <expan>gelawbe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd vns in <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>ſache<ex>n</ex></expan> . eẅr gnade vnd guten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_118_r1l23"><expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> beweıſen wellet als wır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ſunderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> wol getrawen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_118_r1l24">das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır vmb eẅr <expan>mechtık<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>wıllıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> vnd gern <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dıenen</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_118_r1l25"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_118" id="58r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, grefen zu Velldencz und
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> zu Meysenheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns hat <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> lieber
                                <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und ratgeselle Wilhelm Mendell wol
                        gesagt, wie sich ewr mechtikeit, als er mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> nehst zu Frankfurt von des handels
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>zwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan> Stepfan von
                        Peyern, und unser von <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> ein seinr
                                <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> jüdinn und einr jüdinn bey uns
                        wonhaft geredt hab, <expan>gnediklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab beweiset, des
                        wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> mechtikeit
                            <expan>fleissikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> danken und williklich begern
                            <expan>zu v<ex>er</ex></expan>dienen. Also schiken wir
                                <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Wilhelm Mendell zu
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>, dem wir befolhen
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> bas von <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan> zu reden, und <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        ewr <expan>mechtik<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit fleiss, was
                                <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> ratgeselle in
                            <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan> zu disem mal von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an ewr gnade <expan>w<ex>er</ex>be</expan>,
                        daz ir in umb <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan> darinn günstiklich
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan>, im des genczlich
                                <expan>gelawbe<ex>n</ex></expan> und uns in
                                <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan> ewr gnade und guten
                            <expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan> beweisen wellet, als wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>sunderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> wol getrawen. Das
                            <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir umb ewr
                            <expan>mechtik<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>willikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> und gern
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
